I"ê<h2 id="bloatware-reduction-via-file-descriptors">Bloatware Reduction via File Descriptors</h2>

<p>Original problem</p>
<ol>
  <li>write to a file, or,</li>
  <li>write to console</li>
</ol>

<p>Bloatware solution (psuedo-code):</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>if (output === 'file') {
    file.write (...)
} else if (output === 'console') {
    console.log (...)
}
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="bloatware-reduction">Bloatware Reduction</h2>

<p>Invent <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">file descriptors</code> and let underlying machinery figure out what to do:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>fd.write (...)
</code></pre></div></div>

